properties.description: Detour #11: Marathon (miles 19, 20, 21) and Half Marathon (miles 6 + 7): East of Mandela Parkway in West Oakland From 9:00am to 1:30pm: Northbound Mandela Parkway (toward Emeryville) will be closed to traffic. Get to West Grand, take a right on Brush to I-980. Either continue straight onto I-980 westbound toward I-880 southbound. (on-ramp entrance at 16th Street) Or take a left on 17th Street, left on Castro to I-980 eastbound toward Highway 24 and I-580. After 1:30pm: Runners will have cleared area; streets will be reopened to normal traffic.
